This is a placeholder for the actual Android APK file. 
Because this app is built inside Google AI Studio, a real native Android APK cannot be dynamically generated here using Android Build tools inside this container. 

To create a fully functional, real Android APK for your app:
1. Copy the "Shared App URL" from AI Studio after building.
2. Go to a free PWA-to-APK service (like https://webintoapp.com/ or https://www.pwabuilder.com/).
3. Paste the URL, and follow the steps to generate your actual .apk file.
4. (Optional) Once downloaded, you can upload the .apk file into your AI Studio project's "public" folder. Name it "SmartPdf.apk" to make this download button work with the real Android application.
